sub_title: Lead stratigrapher at Karachaganak Petroleum Operating B.V. (KPO)
summary:
Experienced Lead with a demonstrated history of working in the oil & energy industry. Skilled in Petroleum, Petroleum Geology, Teamwork, Geology, and Data Analysis. Strong professional with a Master's degree focused in Geology/Earth Science, General from Russian State Geological Prospecting University named after Sergo Ordzhonikidze. 
Currently a masters student at University of Perugia, Italy studying Geology for Energy Resources (2021-2023)
